# Google Analytics Configuration
# Get your Measurement ID from Google Analytics (format: G-XXXXXXXXXX)
VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-PLACEHOLDER

# To enable Google Analytics:
# 1. Create a .env.local file (same directory as this file)
# 2. Copy this content and replace G-PLACEHOLDER with your actual Measurement ID
# 3. Commit .env.local to .gitignore (it's already there)
# 4. Google Analytics will automatically start tracking page views and form submissions
